latestPosts.caption:
Chloé in Capri
 
Discover our new ephemeral boutique in Capri.
 
Rooted in sculptural architecture, the boutique design balances form and function, featuring organic curves that reflect a Mediterranean sensibility.
 
Opening with the first High Summer collection, Chloé à la Plage, the Capri boutique is open all summer. 
 
Chloé in Capri
Via Camerelle 71, Capri
Open daily from 10:00 AM to 9:00 PM

Photographed by @alexandreguirkinger 
 
#Chloe #ChemenaKamali
